DarkMouse::

(O_o)
She could almost feel her jaw hit the floor with a thud. She could 
feel her whiskers turning pink.  "You...like...me?"  She thought 
about this for a second. Despite the fact that she was very 
flattered, her logic circuits told her that was mathematically 
impossable since they had just met, or had they. She smiled and 
blushed slightly. "UH, well then. I guess I should stay here then and 
see what I can do around here untill I get my circuits in order."  
She went over and started looking at the hologram more closely. "So 
this is where the old pack used to be?" she said pointing to a small 
speck on the map.
